data.description: Welcome to this charming bungalow in the highly sought after heart of Seminole Heights! Don't miss out on this spacious 4 bedroom, 2 bath home on a HUGE lot. Electrical, plumbing, flooring, water heater, insulation, and cabinets replaced in 2018. New AC unit installed in 2019, interior paint completed in July 2021! On the first floor, you'll find a large Master Bedroom with an updated ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet. Down the hall is a second spacious bedroom. With an open concept family room, dining room and kitchen, this home is a perfect entertaining space. Make this oversized back yard your dream oasis. Plenty of room for a large pool, outdoor kitchen and even a firepit - the possibilities are endless. Centrally located to all restaurants, bars and local highlights of Seminole Heights, such as Nebraska Mini Mart, Hair of the Dog Park Bar, Old Heights Bistro, Ella's, and Ebisu Sushi Shack. Tampa International Airport is just 10 minutes away, and Zoo Tampais  5 minutes away. Set up your showing today!
